	<a href="http://www.webreference.com/authoring/languages/xml/rss/intro/2.html">Introduction to RSS: Syndication and Aggregation</a>.&nbsp; A little whatzitabout article, with a discussion of aggregator services and also reference to the meerkat technical aggregator.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#108103263077753037">Saturday, April 03, 2004</a></span></div>
